.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH DELPHI-TRACE 1  "delphitools-cli 0.1.0" "delphitools manual"
.SH NAME
trace \- Trace raster images to SVG vectors
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBtrace\fR [\fB\-\-preset\fR] [\fB\-\-colours\fR] [\fB\-\-blur\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIIMAGE\fR> 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Trace raster images to SVG vectors
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-preset\fR \fI<PRESET>\fR [default: default]
Preset: default, detailed, posterize
.TP
\fB\-\-colours\fR \fI<COLOURS>\fR
Number of colours (overrides preset)
.TP
\fB\-\-blur\fR \fI<BLUR>\fR [default: 0]
Pre\-blur radius
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
<\fIIMAGE\fR>

